<td width="34%" style="text-align:center;font-size:90%;"><a href="#Bible_du_Rabbinat_1899/JérémieSommaire">Sommaire</a></td>
<td width="33%" style="text-align:right;font-size:90%;"><a href="/wiki/Bible_du_Rabbinat_1899/%C3%89z%C3%A9chiel" title="Bible du Rabbinat 1899/Ézéchiel">Ézéchiel</a><span class="%5B%5BBible+du+Rabbinat+1899%2F%C3%89z%C3%A9chiel%7C%C3%89z%C3%A9chiel%5D%5DhiddenStructure" style="color:#808080">&#160;&#160;►</span></td>
